<CONTENT>
<DEFINITIONTABLE>
  <ROW><TERM><CODEROUTINE><X><T>xargs</T><A>https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man1/xargs.1.html</A><L>en</L><F>HTML</F></X> &lt;command&gt;</CODEROUTINE></TERM><DESC>build and execute command</DESC></ROW>
  <ROW><TERM><CODEROUTINE>cat foobar | xargs -n 1 ls -l</CODEROUTINE></TERM><DESC>long list of files defined in <CODEROUTINE>foobar</CODEROUTINE></DESC></ROW>
  <ROW><TERM><CODEROUTINE>xargs -P &lt;n&gt;</CODEROUTINE><BR/><CODEROUTINE>xargs --max-procs=&lt;n&gt;</CODEROUTINE></TERM><DESC>run up to &lt;n&gt; process simultaneously<BR/>take care with shared resources, in particular the output could be garbaged</DESC></ROW>
</DEFINITIONTABLE>
<BR/>
<BR/>
<DEFINITIONTABLE>
<ROW><TERM><CODEROUTINE><X><T>tty</T><A>https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man1/tty.1.html</A><L>en</L><F>HTML</F></X></CODEROUTINE></TERM><DESC>print the file name of the terminal connected to standard input</DESC></ROW>
</DEFINITIONTABLE>
