  <ROW><TERM><CODEROUTINE><X><T>users</T><A>https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man1/users.1.html</A><L>en</L><F>HTML</F></X></CODEROUTINE></TERM><DESC>print login names of users currently logged in</DESC></ROW>
